Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.37,0:00:02.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Waiting gets us nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.77,0:00:04.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take a step forward into the future...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.08,0:00:05.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Begin the deduction and love countdown!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.34,0:00:07.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A case at a beauty salon...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.59,0:00:10.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will the suspect gain a powerful edge through the testimony of a lawyer?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.67,0:00:12.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.17,0:00:13.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A child with the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.93,0:00:15.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.97,0:00:19.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I left it to the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.22,0:02:02.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, onto the next item.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.43,0:02:06.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The fighter Nagasaku Shirou is preparing for the championship bout next month, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.77,0:02:08.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like his wedding is rapidly approaching too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.06,0:02:12.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Young people are always at their best before they get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.48,0:02:15.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? Stop being such a grouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.65,0:02:19.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the other hand, Dad, you need to be getting ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.45,0:02:22.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't we agree to have dinner at 10:00?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.24,0:02:24.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's only 6:30!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.08,0:02:28.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We need to leave early so we can go and pick up Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.58,0:02:29.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pick up?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.58,0:02:31.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At her office?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.33,0:02:33.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the beauty salon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.46,0:02:34.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The beauty salon!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.63,0:02:36.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.42,0:02:39.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The reason we're having dinner so late at 10:00 is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.43,0:02:41.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So she can have her hair cut!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.72,0:02:42.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.85,0:02:45.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's getting all dressed up for you, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.56,0:02:48.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.56,0:02:50.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just so she can look cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.94,0:02:54.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should dress nicely too, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.61,0:02:56.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.69,0:02:59.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, you get washed up too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.20,0:03:00.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're getting dressed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.32,0:03:08.95,Title,,0,0,0,,LAWYER KISAKI ERI'S TESTIMONY\N(PART ONE)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.26,0:03:22.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This was the last thing I expected to be doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.51,0:03:23.84,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Hasaka Minayo (29)\NBeautician
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.22,0:03:25.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.64,0:03:29.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I still plan to have you cut my hair even after I'm married.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.80,0:03:29.10,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Nagasaku Shirou (28)\NFighter
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.89,0:03:32.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If she knew you were frequenting the beauty salon of your former girlfriend...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.06,0:03:35.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your beautiful TV star wife would get angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.15,0:03:41.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's why we're cutting my hair here in the bathroom rather than in sight out in the salon, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.40,0:03:45.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm just being considerate to a popular fighter who's about to get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.37,0:03:47.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But look...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.37,0:03:48.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's already 8:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.87,0:03:49.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Customers aren't going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.83,0:03:51.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.08,0:03:54.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.88,0:03:56.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.29,0:03:58.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.88,0:04:00.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's already closing time, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:02.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.17,0:04:04.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The thing is, someone made a special appointment for tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.26,0:04:08.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't mind coming back some other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.72,0:04:10.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't really need to have this done by today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.89,0:04:13.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Today's the last time...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.19,0:04:16.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The last time I cut your hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.23,0:04:20.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Welcome, Kisaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.53,0:04:22.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.99,0:04:25.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm always having to come in at such a late hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.91,0:04:26.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.74,0:04:28.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're alone tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.20,0:04:31.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the rest of the staff had things to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.83,0:04:37.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just so you don't feel lonely, I'll raise the volume of the BGM for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.46,0:04:38.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.63,0:04:40.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't have to go to all that fuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.72,0:04:47.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You want the usual color, cut, and perm, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.10,0:04:51.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As for the cut, you only need to straighten out the ends a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.06,0:04:55.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, to start with we'll wash your hair over at the shampoo stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.94,0:05:00.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.57,0:05:02.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why am I, the renowned detective, Mouri Kogoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.40,0:05:08.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Being forced to go to a beauty salon at a time like this and pick up some old woman who's leisurely getting her hair cut?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.33,0:05:10.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's no problem, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:11.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, we have the spare time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.33,0:05:15.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom said she got an appointment for 8:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.00,0:05:18.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So we might get to see Mom with her hair down for the first time in a long while.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.13,0:05:22.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was already tired of seeing that when we were young.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.17,0:05:27.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yet despite that, you agreed pretty quickly to go pick her up, Uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.97,0:05:31.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,OK, the coloring's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.10,0:05:35.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, I'll leave you here for about ten minutes while the color sets.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.64,0:05:36.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please remain like you are for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.85,0:05:40.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're going out somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.36,0:05:41.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.11,0:05:42.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just to the convenience store to put out the garbage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.15,0:05:44.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.23,0:05:46.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was thinking we could exchange gossip like usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.74,0:05:47.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.07,0:05:51.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I've always looked forward to that each time too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.87,0:05:54.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like the stories of your defense trials...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.29,0:05:57.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the ones about your famous detective husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.79,0:06:02.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I have plans to see that famous detective for the first time in a while after this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.71,0:06:05.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be sure to stock up on some of his good stories for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.38,0:06:08.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow! I'll have to put more effort than usual into your setting!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.51,0:06:12.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can hear your fond stories about your husband while I'm cutting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.35,0:06:15.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not fondness, just idle complaints...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.94,0:06:22.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I remember correctly, the beauty salon is somewhere at the top of this hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.77,0:06:27.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since this is your first time seeing her in a while, please talk nicely, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.78,0:06:31.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, today especially I'll be giving that woman a whacking...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.87,0:06:41.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that sound just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.46,0:06:46.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We just heard the sound of something being hit and then falling, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.63,0:06:49.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, I don't see anything around that's fallen...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.88,0:06:52.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think we hit anything with the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.80,0:06:53.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could that be it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.97,0:06:57.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, down there on top of the garbage collection point.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.14,0:07:00.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.07,0:07:07.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.07,0:07:07.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A person!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.94,0:07:10.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,J-Just in case, I'll call for an ambulance and the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.07,0:07:14.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.87,0:07:15.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.79,0:07:19.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.54,0:07:24.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks, it's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.59,0:07:26.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks for being a good customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.71,0:07:30.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, isn't it a little bit noisy outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.80,0:07:32.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like something happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.05,0:07:35.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard the sound of a patrol car as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.10,0:07:37.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Should we go have a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.89,0:07:39.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.52,0:07:42.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, if it's a case, that's more my husband's department.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.98,0:07:43.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.86,0:07:47.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's most important to me is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.23,0:07:49.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your defense...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.03,0:07:51.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lawyer Kisaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.82,0:07:54.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.03,0:07:55.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.58,0:07:59.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to his driver's license...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.95,0:08:02.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The deceased is Nagasaku Shirou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, age 28.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.54,0:08:06.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The cause of death is blood loss due to the severing of his carotid artery.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.59,0:08:12.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Based on Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s story about happening to hear the sound of something falling...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.63,0:08:14.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After someone sliced open his neck...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.51,0:08:19.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They tossed him over the guardrail of the road above and into here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.97,0:08:23.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, when we heard the sound on the road above...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.23,0:08:26.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We didn't see anyone else around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.15,0:08:28.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.36,0:08:29.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.53,0:08:30.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.98,0:08:38.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We should consider that they could have carried the body on a tall vehicle, like a truck, and threw it from atop the trailer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.16,0:08:41.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, I don't think we heard the sound of a truck or anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.95,0:08:42.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess not...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.75,0:08:44.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What we heard was...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.92,0:08:47.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The sound of a "whack," from something being hit...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.00,0:08:49.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A "thud," from something falling...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.42,0:08:53.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And a "klink klink," like something rolling. Those three sounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.88,0:08:57.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A "whack," a "thud," and "klink klink?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.76,0:09:01.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, leaving the sounds aside, if we assume the body was thrown...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.81,0:09:04.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's highly probable that the culprit is a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.23,0:09:09.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And not just an ordinary one, but a reasonably skilled hand-to-hand fighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.44,0:09:10.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fighter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.07,0:09:12.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't recognize him, Inspector?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.78,0:09:18.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The victim is a fighter scheduled to compete in the next championship: Nagasaku Shirou.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.41,0:09:22.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's a fighter known for not letting his opponent get behind him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.58,0:09:23.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His weight class is 90 kg.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.62,0:09:27.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To slice the neck of a guy like this and to throw him easily...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.46,0:09:30.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They must have been considerably quick-witted and strongly muscled.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.59,0:09:35.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it's only slicing his neck, couldn't a woman have done it too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.01,0:09:38.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Depending on the situation at the time of this man's murder, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.97,0:09:44.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eri!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.93,0:09:45.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.35,0:09:48.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's my line.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.31,0:09:51.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The café we're having dinner at isn't near here, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.40,0:09:53.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.48,0:09:55.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.15,0:09:58.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, at any rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.95,0:10:01.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the victim was a fighter...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.49,0:10:04.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's check to see if there's some fellow fighter that had a grudge against him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.00,0:10:08.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stupid police...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.08,0:10:11.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sniff around his colleagues all you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.84,0:10:13.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter how hard you look...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.38,0:10:18.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll never arrive at an ordinary beautician like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.85,0:10:24.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Miss, you're from this neighborhood, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.77,0:10:27.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.60,0:10:30.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there a barber shop or beauty salon nearby?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.65,0:10:33.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.77,0:10:35.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you asking her something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.57,0:10:36.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.28,0:10:39.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you look at that dead man's neck...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.61,0:10:44.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll see a lot of small cut-off pieces of hair mixed in with the blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.70,0:10:46.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.50,0:10:54.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.25,0:11:01.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was thinking that maybe he was getting his hair cut before he was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.80,0:11:02.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.10,0:11:03.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And also...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.35,0:11:08.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't the blood that flowed along his neck strangely broken in places?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.02,0:11:12.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.98,0:11:19.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that because his neck was cut when he was wearing a cape or towel from when you get a haircut?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.74,0:11:20.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.32,0:11:25.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it was a barber or beautician, even if the victim were a seasoned fighter...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.99,0:11:31.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means they could bring a blade against their open neck from behind without raising suspicion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.09,0:11:36.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it, Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.80,0:11:38.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.26,0:11:42.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} noticed something strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.85,0:11:47.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.10,0:11:52.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that means it's quite likely that the culprit is a some macho barber or beautician, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.98,0:11:53.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.15,0:11:56.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then they could easily carry this man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.02,0:12:03.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll go find out if there's any person to answer that description in the neighborhood...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.82,0:12:05.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, why not ask her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.78,0:12:07.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She might know...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.87,0:12:11.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because I'm sure that woman is a barber or beautician.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.29,0:12:12.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.54,0:12:14.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.29,0:12:16.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.96,0:12:17.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.09,0:12:20.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.96,0:12:22.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the hell is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.14,0:12:31.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because I'm sure that woman is a barber or beautician.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.02,0:12:32.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.85,0:12:33.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.77,0:12:36.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.77,0:12:38.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.02,0:12:39.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.23,0:12:43.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was cutting my hair until just a moment ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.90,0:12:47.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, the beauty salon you had an appointment at today was...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.99,0:12:49.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was Hasaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s salon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.20,0:12:53.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems it was originally founded by her late father.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.87,0:12:56.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's remarkable that you noticed, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.46,0:12:58.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That she was a beautician, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.42,0:12:59.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was her hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.46,0:13:04.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a callus on the second joint of the ring finger on that lady's right hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.01,0:13:05.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.93,0:13:07.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you please show me your right hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.26,0:13:10.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.97,0:13:12.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.31,0:13:19.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's known as a scissors callus, which develops from always placing your right finger through the loop of the scissors.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.82,0:13:24.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, if you look closely, you'll see her nails are turning a light brownish color.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.74,0:13:31.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's from the chemicals she's always using to dye and shampoo her customer's hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.66,0:13:33.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How do you know all that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.37,0:13:37.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They did that on a TV program about beauticians!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.33,0:13:40.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Again with the TV?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.09,0:13:42.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You watch that too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.71,0:13:45.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a lot better than your listening to horse racing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.84,0:13:47.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Horse racing is like romance for men!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.26,0:13:49.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.39,0:13:57.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, let me ask you, do you know how many barber shops and beauty salons are in the area?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.85,0:13:59.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.23,0:14:04.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The victim, Nagasaku Shirou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, was a 90 kg fighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.78,0:14:09.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} and his family just happened to be passing by, they heard the sound of a "thud" from something falling.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.28,0:14:17.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, since there are a lot of small hairs of his same blond color clinging to the blood around his neck...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.87,0:14:21.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And based on how the blood is strangely broken up...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.63,0:14:26.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit cut open Nagasaku{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s neck with a blade while in the middle of cutting his hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.05,0:14:30.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then we have to assume he was thrown from somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.93,0:14:40.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you don't mind, we hope you can tell us if there are any barbers or beauticians in the area who have the strength to have carried him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.94,0:14:41.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.81,0:14:44.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are two or three other shops besides ours, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.11,0:14:48.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure if they have anyone who has that kind of strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.32,0:14:50.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were mean, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.74,0:14:57.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because when I asked earlier if there were any barbers or beauty salons nearby...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.29,0:14:59.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You didn't answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.71,0:15:04.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you tell me then that you had your own beauty salon?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.09,0:15:06.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.25,0:15:10.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wasn't it you who was mean? Asking that when you already knew the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.55,0:15:11.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.68,0:15:12.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"But" nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.60,0:15:18.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, watch this brat properly so he doesn't wander around.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.48,0:15:20.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.56,0:15:25.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't answer immediately because I was agitated.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.86,0:15:26.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Agitated?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.23,0:15:31.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because when I arrived, I recognized the dead man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.78,0:15:33.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-You knew him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.57,0:15:35.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The victim, Nagasaku{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.03,0:15:39.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you'll learn about it later, so I'll tell you about it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.12,0:15:45.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He and I were classmates in high school and we dated for a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.67,0:15:48.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, Nagasaku{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} had been to your shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.05,0:15:49.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.13,0:15:53.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before he got engaged, he used to come a lotto get his hair cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.43,0:15:54.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Engaged?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.05,0:15:57.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, that was reported in a sports newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.01,0:16:00.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, that makes it even more likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.69,0:16:03.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hasaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.02,0:16:06.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You had a motive to kill Nagasaku{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} as well, did you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.28,0:16:11.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.74,0:16:13.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How did you pull that one out of the bushes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.20,0:16:19.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His estranged former girlfriend lives near the area where the body was discovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.91,0:16:21.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Obviously she's the one to suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.91,0:16:23.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm amazed at your hasty thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.92,0:16:25.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Takagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.38,0:16:29.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was the presumed time of death?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.38,0:16:31.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.59,0:16:33.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} discovered the body at...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.34,0:16:36.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sometime around 8:30 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.22,0:16:40.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it would have to be around twenty minutes before that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.60,0:16:43.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, it was impossible for her to be the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.73,0:16:49.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because she was caring for my hair the whole time from 8:00 PM until after 9:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.19,0:16:52.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was really with you the whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.99,0:16:55.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was somewhere near me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.74,0:16:59.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, midway through she went out to do something, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.28,0:17:01.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It only took ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.41,0:17:04.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, she must have cleverly used those ten minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.33,0:17:04.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.50,0:17:09.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her beauty salon is on the top of that hill, way up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.50,0:17:13.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's too far to for her to have carried an adult man with a sliced neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.01,0:17:15.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.26,0:17:17.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this "but still?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.27,0:17:25.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom and Dad are glaring at each other again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.40,0:17:32.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if what Kisaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} just said is true...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.98,0:17:33.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.78,0:17:37.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you like, why don't you come check my shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.25,0:17:48.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess this is OK once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.00,0:17:54.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take a left turn at the next intersection.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.63,0:17:59.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.59,0:18:03.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you going to turn at an intersection, you need signal ahead of time and check both ways!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.26,0:18:04.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can't you follow the rules properly?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.18,0:18:06.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.06,0:18:08.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is why I told you not to ride in my car!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.60,0:18:11.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My shop is right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.36,0:18:11.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.74,0:18:19.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.53,0:18:22.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeez, such reckless driving.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.20,0:18:25.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I should have just walked here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.54,0:18:28.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.63,0:18:31.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.13,0:18:34.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, Kisaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, you were sitting in this chair...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.71,0:18:37.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And Hasaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was cutting your hair, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.59,0:18:38.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.63,0:18:41.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She always cuts my hair after work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.10,0:18:44.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I made an appointment for 8:00 P.M. today as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.43,0:18:46.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I came to the shop at 8:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.27,0:18:50.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From there we started with a shampoo for ten minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.81,0:18:52.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Coloring for twenty minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.02,0:18:54.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Another shampoo for ten minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.98,0:18:56.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then a perm for ten minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.15,0:18:58.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yet one more shampoo for ten minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.28,0:19:00.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then fifteen minutes for the cut...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.16,0:19:02.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the last shampoo for ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.32,0:19:05.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With ten more minutes for blow drying and setting...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.20,0:19:08.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That makes it about an hour and a half, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.58,0:19:10.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.83,0:19:12.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You remember things extremely well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.42,0:19:15.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what I've always done.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.50,0:19:20.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was supposed to have dinner with someone tonight after this, so I looked at my watch a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.97,0:19:25.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When she went out to do something midway through, when was it and where did she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.64,0:19:28.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was while we were waiting until the coloring had set.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.35,0:19:34.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure she left for about ten minutes between 8:20 and 8:30, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.40,0:19:40.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ten minutes between 8:20 and 8:30, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.61,0:19:44.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then she must have used that time to kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.62,0:19:48.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't take three minutes to get back here from the scene by car.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.62,0:19:49.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.00,0:19:52.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't have a driver's license.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.08,0:19:55.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I only went to the convenience store to throw out the trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.96,0:19:56.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The trash?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.17,0:20:01.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To the collection point that's just across from the convenience store where go to I buy things.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.42,0:20:02.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Convenience store?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.51,0:20:06.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's really close, so would you like to go check it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.77,0:20:09.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.27,0:20:11.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this a back road?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.64,0:20:15.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This route is shorter than going down the main street.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.36,0:20:17.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And this scooter?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.19,0:20:21.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's something my father left me, I use it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.03,0:20:24.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I use it sometimes when I go to that convenience store...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.61,0:20:25.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like when I buy rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.82,0:20:29.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, you put the body on the back of the scooter and...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.83,0:20:30.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.04,0:20:31.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What now!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.37,0:20:36.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even putting a 90 kg man on the back would be difficult...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.67,0:20:40.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But how could she drive around with him set up like that without anyone noticing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.38,0:20:45.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And how do you explain her throwing him like that in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.59,0:20:48.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was just speaking hypothetically...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.52,0:20:53.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And so, which way is the convenience store?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.35,0:20:53.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.56,0:20:58.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you go down that side street, it comes out right in front of the convenience store.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.23,0:21:04.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does this way maybe lead to the garbage collection point where the body was?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.24,0:21:05.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.53,0:21:09.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.08,0:21:16.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.50,0:21:21.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The garbage collection point where the body was is two levels directly below here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.09,0:21:28.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, to toss a person from here to the garbage point would be impossible without using a crane...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.10,0:21:33.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The popular fighter Nagasaku Shirou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was killed...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.81,0:21:35.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And his body was found at the garbage collection point.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.23,0:21:39.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At that time, we heard three sounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.78,0:21:46.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What on earth could those sounds have been?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.99,0:21:52.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nagasaku{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was killed while he was having his hair cut at a barber shop or beauty salon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.79,0:21:55.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Therefore the most suspicious person is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.87,0:21:58.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one who runs a beauty salon in the neighborhood, Hasaka Minayo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.42,0:22:02.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Minayo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was Nagasaku{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s former girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.00,0:22:05.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, between 8:00 and 9:00, Minayo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.17,0:22:07.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cutting Kisaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}'s hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.72,0:22:10.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was only away from Kisaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}'s side...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.39,0:22:13.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For only ten minutes starting at 8:20.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.97,0:22:16.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we assume Minayo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.85,0:22:22.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How did she move Nagasaku{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s 90 kg corpse to the garbage collection point in a mere 10 minutes?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.57,0:22:26.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is Minayo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} really the culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.53,0:22:28.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.95,0:22:32.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The origins of those three sounds we heard...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.46,0:24:01.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The dust on the pole of this road sign...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.54,0:24:04.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Has been rubbed off, and there's a thin stripe.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.79,0:24:07.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where'd this stripe come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.84,0:24:10.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were hurt, I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.59,0:24:11.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.34,0:24:13.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We refuse...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.22,0:24:17.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unless you can provide us with an arrest warrant issued by the court?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.10,0:24:20.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, what if I show you proof?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.31,0:24:23.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Proof that she was capable of performing the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.98,0:24:29.94,Title,,0,0,0,,LAWYER KISAKI ERI'S TESTIMONY\N(PART TWO)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.28,0:24:32.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.82,0:24:34.95,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Scooter
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.20,0:24:36.24,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I'm clueless.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.24,0:24:37.49,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Did you try the barber?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.49,0:24:37.87,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.87,0:24:38.95,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,It's always refreshing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.95,0:24:39.66,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Hey!
